comment: LATR shows Covington (PHI) makes contact with Acy's (SAC) arm, affecting his shot attempt.
LATR shows Collison (SAC) establishes himself legally in Smith's (PHI) path and contact by Smith is incidental to the screen.
Okafor (PHI) makes contact with Cousins' (SAC) arm that affects his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Gay (SAC) makes contact with Covington's (PHI) arm that affects his jump shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Convington (PHI) was not behind the three-point line when he was fouled is upheld.
Smith (PHI) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Cousins' (SAC) drive, absorbing the contact initiated by Cousins.
Collison (SAC) commits a take foul on Smith (PHI).
Canaan (PHI) commits a take foul on Collison (SAC).
